# MoveToJointTarget Service Definition
#
# Commands MoveIt to move to a joint-space goal.
#
# Request:
#   - joint_names: Names of the joints to move (must match the MoveIt planning group).
#   - positions: Target positions for the corresponding joint_names.
#   - execute: If true, plan and execute. If false, plan only.
#
# Response:
#   - success: True if planning (and execution if requested) succeeded.
#   - message: Human-readable result/diagnostic message.

string[] joint_names
float64[] positions
bool execute
---
bool success
string message
